      "name": "Ayush Rajesh Jhaveri",
      "image": "/images/people/AyushRJ.jpeg",
      "bio": "I\u2019m a Master\u2019s student in Computer Science at NYU Courant. My research focuses on reasoning in large language models, particularly on improving hypothesis exploration, with inspiration from cognitive science.",
